The Enugu Electricity Distribution (EEDC) has promoted 164 staff from its workforce. A statement by its Head of Communications, Mr. Emeka Ezeh in Enugu, noted that the gesture was in keeping with its commitment towards professional development of its employees. Also, he stated that a total of 178 staff of the organisation received step increases, while 1,661 had their appointments confirmed. Ezeh added that the company had sponsored 12 of its staff to India, for training.